nks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 about <a href=\"/best-reverse-mortgages\">Reverse Mortgages</a> here.</em>","Proficio Reverse Mortgage is the reverse mortgage arm of Proficio Mortgage. Proficio is based in Orlando, Florida, and is licensed to operate across the country. Based on its share of the market, Proficio is one of the top 10 reverse mortgage lenders in the country.","If you want an estimate for what you might expect from a reverse mortgage from Proficio, the company asks that you submit your name and phone number and wait for representatives to follow up. The website lacks an online calculator or any other tool to give you an estimate of the payout you could expect from a reverse mortgage.","Proficio has a wealth of educational resources and information about reverse mortgages. What really stands out is the depth of the material available for the heirs and children of seniors who are borrowing through a reverse mortgage. Often it is the children who have to deal with repercussions and repayment of a reverse mortgage, and Proficio does well with providing them with information about what to expect.","This reverse mortgage lender also provides good information for the seniors seeking a reverse mortgage, in particular warning them to avoid ancillary services that might request things like lender referral fees. There are also many testimonials on the Proficio website of customers who report being happy with their reverse mortgages.","Proficio offers a variety of reverse mortgage products. The Standard-fixed rate is its most popular, offering a fixed insurance rate across the duration of the loan. There is also an adjustable-rate variant of the Standard loan for those who want to hedge against inflation.","In addition, Proficio offers Saver loans, with both fixed and adjustable rates. The Saver loans have many of the same features as the Standard but with lower principle and lower closing costs. These loans are ideal if you&#39;re looking for a reverse mortgage in order to borrow a smaller amount for home repairs or some other large expense.","As one of the top reverse mortgage lenders in the country by volume, Proficio Reverse Mortgage stands apart for the depth of information it offers to the children of borrowers. Proficio offers a variety of borrowing options and educational resources for anyone interested in reverse mortgages."]},"id":"1f6f8618-4736-4553-b1a6-5cdb1c2042f2","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_63922","url":"/proficio-reverse-mortgage-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"sabrina-rojas-weiss","url":"/author/sabrina-rojas-weiss","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Sabrina Rojas Weiss","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"tVZv6ejiouijuHU3n7n49Y","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-04-02T22:39:26Z","datePublished":"2015-04-02T22:39:26Z","name":"Proficio Reverse Mortgage","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 about Reverse Mortgages here. Proficio Reverse Mortgage is the reverse mortgage arm of Proficio Mortgage.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 about Reverse Mortgages here. Proficio Reverse Mortgage is the reverse mortgage arm of Proficio Mortgage.","language":"en","dateModified":"2015-04-02T22:39:26Z","id":"adLRGySMczYfrhnDjyVf26","meta":{"title":"Proficio Reverse Mortgage Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"Read our unbiased review of Proficio Reverse Mortgage. See how Proficio Reverse Mortgage compares to the best Reverse Mortgages."},"products":[{"slug":"proficio-rever